=A0That would be the funniest possible outcome, much funnier than Musk just=
 changing his mind again.=C2=A0Musk is a business prankster and his antics =
are getting old, but for a serious Morgan Stanley banker to show up and do =
the bot routine, with a straight face,=C2=A0would be incredible.</p></block=
quote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But I think the chances of this are slim. In g=
eneral, it is very bad form for banks to try to back out of their debt fina=
