: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> told the judge</a> that =E2=80=9Cthe Deb=
t Financing parties have indicated that they are prepared to honor their co=
mmitments=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9Care working cooperatively to fund the close=
.=E2=80=9D It would be=C2=A0hard for the banks to walk back on that. And ev=
eryone knows =E2=80=94=C2=A0I=E2=80=99ve been saying it for months, and now=
 Musk is more or less admitting it =E2=80=94=C2=A0that <em>Musk=E2=80=99s</=
em> arguments for getting out of the deal were ridiculous, so it would be r=
idiculous for the banks to try them. They will swallow hard and put up the =
money.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That said, it will take them some time. Musk=
=E2=80=99s motion says:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Defendants are working diligently,=
 cooperatively, and in good faith with the financing banks to prepare for t=
he closing. That funding, however, will take time because the parties are w=
orking through the complex process of arranging $12.5 billion dollars of de=
bt financing, including drafting required documentation, arranging security=
 interests for a portion of the debt financing, and finalizing funding mech=
anics. Understandably, that cannot happen before the October 17 trial.=C2=
=A0=E2=80=A6 Counsel for the financing banks have estimated they will need =
until October 28 to fund the loans.</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That=E2=80=99s kind of weird? In a perfect wor=
ld, the banks would do two broad sorts of things before funding this deal:<=
/p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Paperwork, and</li>=09<li style=3D"ma=
rgin-bottom: 5px;">Sell most of the debt to investors rather than funding i=
t themselves.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Everything mentioned in Musk=E2=80=99s motion =
=E2=80=94=C2=A0drafting, security interests, funding mechanics =E2=80=94 is=
 in the first category, paperwork, and for enough money you can do any amou=
nt of paperwork in a week by ruining some lawyers=E2=80=99 personal lives. =
I don=E2=80=99t know why it would take until Oct. 28.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On the other hand Musk=E2=80=99s motion does=
=C2=A0<em>not=C2=A0</em>say that the banks plan to=C2=A0<em>market=C2=A0</e=
m>the debt to investors before the closing, and, as we <a href=3D"https://l=
ink.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29299349.282523/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb2=
1iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMTAtMDUvZWxvbi1zLWJhY2s_Y21waWQ9Q=
